#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&smb4k; is an advanced network neighborhood browser and <ulink url="
#| "\"http://www.samba.org\">Samba</ulink> share mounting utility. It "
#| "provides many handy features that ease your life in a &Windows;-dominated "
#| "network environment:"
msgid ""
"&smb4k; is an advanced network neighborhood browser and <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.samba.org\">Samba</ulink> share mounting utility. It provides many handy "
"features that ease your life in a &Windows;-dominated network environment."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; एकः उन्नतः संजालपरिसरस्य ब्राउजर् अस्ति तथा च <ulink url=\"http://www."
"samba.org\">Samba</ulink> साझा माउण्टिङ्ग् उपयोगिता अस्ति । एतत् अनेकानि "
"सुलभविशेषतानि प्रदाति ये &Windows;-प्रधानसंजालवातावरणे भवतः जीवनं सुलभं कुर्वन्ति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This handbook describes &smb4k; 4.0 and to some extent earlier versions."
