msgstr "पूर्वनिर्धारितम् : <guimenuitem>अधः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show custom bookmark label if available"
msgstr "यदि उपलब्धं भवति तर्हि कस्टम् बुकमार्क लेबलं दर्शयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom description (label) of the bookmark is shown. It can be defined "
