#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &smb4k; team would like to thank everyone who contributed by sending "
"patches. Also, a big \"Thank you!\" goes to Rashid N. Achilov "
"<email>shelton@sentry.granch.ru</email>, who convinced us to port &smb4k; to "
"FreeBSD and helped us a great deal to achieve this goal."
msgstr ""
"द &smb4k; team सर्वेषां धन्यवादं दातुम् इच्छति ये patches प्रेषयित्वा योगदानं दत्तवन्तः। "
"अपि च, एकः महत् \"धन्यवादः!\" रशीद एन अचिलोव <email>shelton@sentry.granch.ru</"
"email> इत्यस्मै गच्छति, यः अस्मान् &smb4k; to FreeBSD इत्यस्मै एतत् लक्ष्यं प्राप्तुं बहु "
"साहाय्यं कृतवान् ।"

